## Kairos Frontend — example env
## Copy to `.env` (or configure in Vercel/Railway)

# Backend API base URL
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# Display-only pricing (keep in sync with backend + on-chain AgentRegistry priceWei)
VITE_AGENT_PRICE_BNB=0.0005

# Four.meme Sprint chain config (BNB Chain testnet defaults)
VITE_FOURMEME_RPC_URL=https://data-seed-prebsc-1-s1.binance.org:8545
VITE_FOURMEME_CHAIN_ID=97
VITE_FOURMEME_EXPLORER_BASE=https://testnet.bscscan.com

# Optional: show an Admin badge in the UI
VITE_ADMIN_ADDRESS=

# Reown (WalletConnect) project id for wallet modal (get it from https://dashboard.reown.com)

